ighly multiplexed analysis of serum miRNA. Use of epidural analgesia does alter miRNA profiles, and its effects on mir202-3p, in particular, may explain our previous observation that use of epidural analgesia is associated with a lower rate of ovarian cancer recurrence after primary cytoreductive surgery.},
