s after chemotherapy. Conclusions: This longitudinal study documents moderate neuropsychological deficits together with notable brainspecific structural changes (in GM and WM) in patients with SCLC after chemotherapy and PCI, suggesting that chemotherapy and especially PCI are associated with the development of cognitive and structural brain toxic effects.},
